Package org.omg.CORBA_2_3.portable

Provides methods for the input and output of value types, and contains other updates to the org/omg/CORBA/portable package.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Delegate Delegate class provides the ORB vendor specific implementation of CORBA object.
InputStream InputStream provides for the reading of all of the mapped IDL types from the stream.
ObjectImpl ObjectImpl class is the base class for all stubs.
OutputStream OutputStream provides interface for writing of all of the mapped IDL type to the stream.
